    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>深入体验为喜爱短暂却震撼体验的玩家精心打造的反乌托邦冒险。</strong><br>《Full Void》为您呈现一个人工智能掌控人类未来的扣人心弦的故事。扮演一名孤身少年，在荒废却引人入胜的世界中，仅凭黑客技能努力求生。以精美的手工像素艺术呈现，这款电影式解谜平台游戏虽然篇幅短小，却充满情感深度，带来难以忘怀的游戏旅程，哪怕只需一次畅玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/b780fdc7d8d5d1854a1a2976d3c11b0a.poster.avif?t=1734096524\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/b780fdc7d8d5d1854a1a2976d3c11b0a.webm?t=1734096524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>谜题:</strong><br>在危机四伏的环境中通过黑客技能闯出一条生路，每一步都可能是最后一步。你会选择逃离致命敌人，还是试图控制它们？运用你的技能解谜、探索，并寻找拯救这个崩溃社会的方法。在这个世界里，只有孩子们还拥有自由，但能持续多久？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/f24f0f6e7755dfe353bc890acc7d069b.poster.avif?t=1734096524\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/f24f0f6e7755dfe353bc890acc7d069b.webm?t=1734096524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>电影式冒险:</strong><br>深入一个黑暗世界，在那里，一个失控的人工智能以表面温和却暗藏杀机的方式控制着人类。你将扮演一名在这个充满敌意的反乌托邦未来中依然自由的少年。即使身处恐惧与孤独之中，你也必须坚持前行，揭开这个破碎社会背后的真相。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/d55a25bfd96e6e2c850b569238766d84.poster.avif?t=1734096524\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/d55a25bfd96e6e2c850b569238766d84.webm?t=1734096524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>平台游戏:</strong><br>在手工打造的复古风世界中跳跃穿行，从荒废的城市到阴森的实验室。每一次跳跃都需要勇气，直面未知的挑战。《Full Void》是经典电影式解谜平台游戏《波斯王子》、《Out of This World（Out of This World）》和《Flashback》的精神继承者，结合了现代创新的视觉效果和游戏机制。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/a6dff0684284e18eb2fb700e40b93c0b.apng?t=1734096524\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/a6dff0684284e18eb2fb700e40b93c0b.poster.avif?t=1734096524\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=180 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>复古像素艺术:</strong><br>踏入《Full Void》的16位像素世界，在这里复古美学与现代元素完美融合。体验一款全新的经典之作，既充满怀旧氛围，又带来焕然一新的视觉效果与游戏体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/e4d4d5dc70f591d3bea648e4a86b115a.poster.avif?t=1734096524\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/e4d4d5dc70f591d3bea648e4a86b115a.webm?t=1734096524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>恐怖氛围:</strong><br>沉浸在《Full Void》扣人心弦的环境音效中，体验紧张的恐怖氛围，无需血腥场面。伴随着原创的Amiga MOD音乐，向经典游戏致敬的同时，为你在反乌托邦世界中的每个充满悬念的时刻增添震撼体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859580/extras/c562b3b2c3357b6d19042ca225a20d79.avif?t=1734096524\" width=600 height=347 /></span></p>",
